title: Wonder Woman v1 001-254 260-329 (1942-1986)
description:
For the sake of historical preservation I'm uploading this torrent. This is the first volume of Wonder Woman that was uploaded previously but the series was separated into multiple torrents and they're all dead.

This is the nearly complete first volume of Wonder Woman with the following exceptions. Issues 255 through 259 are missing. They were corrupted in the original torrent. If anyone has them please upload them.

Many thanks to the scanners. They did the hard work. I'm merely uploading it.
